### 创建新数据库新用户：
```
use admin
db.auth("adminxxx","pwdxxx")
use new_db_xxx
db.createuser({user:"usernamexxx",pwd:"userpwdxxx",roles:[{role:"dbOwner",db:"dbnamexxx"}]})
```

### 导入数据：

1. dat 文件
```
mongoimport -h <host>:<port> -u username -p password -d dbname -c collectionanme ../backup/works.dat
``` 
